        <p>A sustainable ecosystem carries great significance for it can affect our behavior,
            culture and
            economic
            practices.</p>
        <br />
        <p><strong>The management of human consumption </strong> as the name indicates, its
            about managing
            how
            much we can take/do without endangering the environment or its ecosystem,
            we as a society must have consideration and ethical behavior to limit ourselves from
            draining
            the
            environment dry as well as be aware of what we produce(from plastics to carbon
            dioxide)
            and find ways to deal with such materials and pollution accordingly.</p>
        <br />
        <p><strong>Ways to help reduce the negative impact we cause:</strong> Asides from the
            obvious which
            will be discussed in the next topic, there are many activities one can do in order
            to help the environment sustain itself from our actions, one of such is for example
            <strong>reforestation</strong>, which has the purpose of restoking the existing
            forests and
            woodlands
            that have been depleted(usualy due to deforestation). Reforestation can also be used
            to rectify
            or
            improve the quality of human life which also further increases our sustainability as
            well
