    <h2>The Importance of recycling</h2>
    <section>
        <p>The most well known action by everyone, something that tends to be taught by primary
            schools/parents and is
            overabundantly showed in television ads.</p>
        <p>A way for us to contribute as a single individual without much effort,
            <strong>recycling</strong>.
        </p>
        <figure>
            <img class="verticalImg" src="./Images/__original_drawn_by_avogado6.jpg" alt="Recycle" height="450"
                width="405">
            <figcaption><a class="link" href=https://twitter.com/i/web/status/1018859005207171072
